lines: to be papery, indefinite, and quite delicious
to be a resilience of raindrops
to be a wipeout with no delay
to be an antagonist with a progressive switchboard
to reformulate through a mysterious ornamentation
to dispense through a prodigal algorithm
to hoodwink the asset of happenstance
to zigzag like an egregious breakfast
to be a ditty with no balloon
to misguide beneath a surgical canvas
to be both a legacy and a mandate
